---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import logo from '../images/logo.png'
---

<article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2 mt-10 justify-between">
  <div>
    <h1 class="md:leading-snug lg:leading-snug leading-normal lg:text-6xl md:text-5xl max-md:text-center text-4xl font-bold mb-10 font-heading">Keep Your Property Looking its Best</h1>
    <p class="text-xl">
      Locally owned Tommy Tree Stump, LLC will keep your property attractive and safe with professional tree services. We specialize in competitively priced stump removal. We will come to your location to bid on the project and keep your property protected while we work. 
      <span class="font-bold">Contact us for a FREE on-site estimate.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <Image src={logo} alt="a tree stump" class="w-[50%] max-md:w-full" />
 
</article>
  


